* Migration Guide to Firebird 3 - eBook
* Firebird Ole Db Driver (alternative for ODBC)
* Jaybird – JDBC driver for Firebird (on github.com)
* Jaybird – JDBC driver for Firebird (on firebirdsql.org)</text><links>
