<doc id="288424" wikidata="Q5160070" url="?curid=288424" title="Confidence, West Virginia">
<text>Confidence is an unincorporated community in Putnam County West Virginia, United States, located on WV 34. The community is served by Confidence Elementary School. Confidence is a part of the Huntington-Ashland Metropolitan Statistical Area (MSA). As of the 2010 census, the MSA had a population of 287,702. New definitions from February 28, 2013 placed the population at 363,000.

